{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"6525e44a-f82c-578c-9ea2-6469fac6f834","html":"<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">docker run --name mongodb-nodejs -d -p 27017:27017 mongo --noauth --bind_ip<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>0.0.0.0</code></pre></div>\n<p>끝 ! ~ 클라이언트 접속 됨.~</p>\n<p>아이디/비번 없음.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>클라이언트는 : mongodb compass community 로 ~\n<a href=\"https://www.mongodb.com/download-center/compass?jmp=hero\">https://www.mongodb.com/download-center/compass?jmp=hero</a></p>\n<p>편의상 윈도우용\nmongodb-compass-community-1.16.3-win32-x64.exe</p>\n<hr>\n<p>컨테이너 내부에 들어가 보려면 ?</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">docker <span class=\"token function\">exec</span> -it mongodb-nodejs <span class=\"token function\">bash</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>os 확인  </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">more</span> /etc/os-release</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"date":"February 11, 2019","title":"초간단 도커 mongodb 설치","description":"초간단 도커 mongodb 설치","tags":["mongodb","docker"]}}},"pageContext":{"id":"6525e44a-f82c-578c-9ea2-6469fac6f834"}}